</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Mornin\" title=\"Mornin\">Mornin</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/East_Blue\" title=\"East Blue\">East Blue</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/East_Blue_Saga#Big_Bird\" title=\"Animal Species/East Blue Saga\">Big Bird</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_40%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nRecently been pouring over comics I read a long time ago. It's weird because just reading them now like this I can recall specific events from my life back then.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n昔、自分がハマってたマンガを最近読みまくってる。一緒に当時の日常まで思い出すから不思議。</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_40%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_39\" title=\"Chapter 39\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_41\" title=\"Chapter 41\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; font